title: China's post-punk rock band Re-TROS Live on KEXP

description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Re-TROS performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded April 06, 2024.

Songs:
HAILING DRUMS 00:33
8+2+8 II 09:47
AT MOSP HERE 19:00

Hua Dong - Vocal, Guitar, Synthesizer
Liu Min - Vocal, Bass, Synthesizer
Huang Jin - Drum, Percussion

Host: Diana Ratsamee

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Jonathan Jacobs & Luke Knecht
